---
title: Black Bean & Roast Veggie Chilli with Garlic Rice, Cucumber Salsa & Corn Chips
description: Get a load of this gently spiced black bean chilli that knows no bounds when it comes to flavour. Sitting on a bed of
garlic-infused rice and served with crunchy corn chips, this is a recipe for a hearty bowl you won’t soon forget.
